\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid8534382\charrsid8534382 Gave Phyllis Karberry Lecture [at Taylorian], organised by Oxford Gender Centre, 1989, celebrating individuals who don\rquote t fit in: Marie Gr\'e9goire
 in Normandy, Mr Busby at Heyford \endash  tape recorded his memories, First World War deserter, Communist, atheist. Upper class anthropologists would not dream of talking to village locals.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid8534382 

