\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid8534382\charrsid8534382 Comments on first chapter of her book. Against anthropology as a fantasy copy of real science \endash  Steven Rose on \lquote Physics envy\rquote 
. Cuts in funding. Believes anthropologic
al method is scientific. Ted Benton and Ian Craib did not push positivist methods. Andy Dawson interviewed staff over 55 and in groups for his thesis, given distinction by Frank Bechhofer, but felt he should pretend the group information came from individ
ual interviews.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid8534382 
