\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid8534382\charrsid8534382 Mother had a series of Caribbean lodgers from late 1950s, through whom
 JO became at ease with people of different cultures. Meeting Malcolm X. As undergraduate JO had relationship with famous Jamaican, Eric Abrams, first black President of Oxford Union. Mixed couple then shocking.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
